*ips_long.

USAGE:
  scw ipam ip <command>

AVAILABLE COMMANDS:
  attach      Attach private IP to custom resource
  create      Reserve a new IP
  delete      Release an IP
  detach      Detach private IP from a custom resource
  get         Get an IP
  list        List existing IPs
  move        Move private IP to a custom resource
  update      Update an IP

FLAGS:
  -h, --help                help for ip
      --list-sub-commands   List all subcommands

GLOBAL FLAGS:
  -c, --config string    The path to the config file
  -D, --debug            Enable debug mode
  -o, --output string    Output format: json or human, see 'scw help output' for more info (default "human")
  -p, --profile string   The config profile to use

Use "scw ipam ip [command] --help" for more information about a command.
